cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV. 

The paper proposes a novel attentional architecture for multi-agent predictive modeling, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The architecture is designed to scale linearly with the number of agents, which is a characteristic of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The method is evaluated on tasks from chess and soccer, which are domains related to computer vision (cs.CV).
